e_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 1891, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "601f7a1d51c62342f755ff90bb7e8141688ae8dae774de5c40f8ce2b20fd8b63", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Our LlamaCloud Services repo has even more examples and notebooks not included here; check out:\r\n  * [LlamaExtract examples](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/tree/main/examples/extract)\r\n  * [LlamaCloudIndex examples](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/tree/main/examples/index)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Starter Notebooks\r\n[Section titled \u201cStarter Notebooks\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/#starter-notebooks)\r\n  * [Parse your first document](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/blob/main/examples/parse/demo_basic.ipynb)\r\n  * [Create your first extraction agent](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/blob/main/examples/extract/resume_screening.ipynb)\r\n  * [Index, search, and chat over your data](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/blob/main/examples/index/getting_started.ipynb)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Advanced Notebooks\r\n[Section titled \u201cAdvanced Notebooks\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/#advanced-notebooks)\r\n  * [Use MultiModal Parsing/Indexing](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/blob/main/examples/parse/demo_advanced.ipynb)\r\n  * [Tour of the JobResult object in LlamaParse](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/blob/main/examples/parse/demo_json_tour.ipynb)\r\n  * [Asset fund analysis with LlamaExtract](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/blob/main/examples/extract/asset_manager_fund_analysis.ipynb)", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 430, "end_char_idx": 1875, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "9951fec0-06c6-49ce-998a-8af6e0ca11f6", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "72468f3a-25ff-41ab-8738-02dedc44d20f", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "b8c39dae2cacf893210786c92b0b022cd8e1ef9c9eefaacca37796940313a1e7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "0812141d-b198-4b6d-872f-4b4f1803352d", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f74a50887f5fef1d15564628f751c9d53793a1bfa0df88013f85ed990bf2a62f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "[Skip to content](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#_top)\r\n# Enterprise Rollout\r\nCopy as Markdown\r\nMCP Server\r\nCopy MCP URL  [ Install in Cursor ](cursor://anysphere.cursor-deeplink/mcp/install?name=llama-index-docs&config=eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2RldmVsb3BlcnMubGxhbWFpbmRleC5haS9tY3AifQ==) Copy Claude config  Copy Codex config \r\n## **Overview**\r\n[Section titled \u201cOverview\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#overview)\r\nRolling out LlamaCloud in a large enterprise requires planning to ensure a seamless onboarding experience for users. This guide provides step-by-step instructions for configuring LlamaCloud for an enterprise environment, defining user roles, setting up integrations, and best practices for operationalizing LlamaCloud in production.\r\nNote that we will be expanding our RBAC offerings, and this cookbook will evolve with additional features\r\n## **Step 1: Setting Up Your Organization**\r\n[Section titled \u201cStep 1: Setting Up Your Organization\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#step-1-setting-up-your-organization)\r\nLlamaCloud structures access and resources using **Organizations** and **Projects**.\r\n### **1.1 Create a Central Organization**\r\n[Section titled \u201c1.1 Create a Central Organization\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#11-create-a-central-organization)\r\n  * Navigate to **Settings**\r\n  * Define a single **organization** for your enterprise (e.g., ACME instead of each user having their own organization).\r\n  * As you scale, you can consider additional organizations. We have seen large enterprises create an organization per business unit.\r\n\r\n\r\n### **1.2 Configure Projects for Departments/ Teams**\r\n[Section titled \u201c1.2 Configure Projects for Departments/ Teams\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#12-configure-projects-for-departments-teams)\r\nEach **Project** serves as a logical unit within the organization.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 2067, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "0812141d-b198-4b6d-872f-4b4f1803352d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "72468f3a-25ff-41ab-8738-02dedc44d20f", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "b8c39dae2cacf893210786c92b0b022cd8e1ef9c9eefaacca37796940313a1e7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "9951fec0-06c6-49ce-998a-8af6e0ca11f6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "f5e5d381f861e3b737e2a26a9d7dc74465c077a653da80b504beb49e80397e7e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "1d1f14a7-6287-45c7-9df2-c00ddf32740a", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "25f324800ab1875e0d185accebf3dca766482f0bc7b3308d7a54315cec959ce4", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Recommended structure:\r\n  * **Experiments** : For initial testing and onboarding\r\n  * **Teams** : Create dedicated projects per Team (e.g., Research, Engineering).\r\n\r\n\r\nNote that integrations are scoped to a project (see below).\r\n## **Step 2: Setting Up Integrations**\r\n[Section titled \u201cStep 2: Setting Up Integrations\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#step-2-setting-up-integrations)\r\nYou can pre-configure integrations to streamline workflows for your users. There are 3 kinds of integrations\r\n  * Embedding Model (e.g. OpenAI keys)\r\n  * Data Sink (e.g. vectorDB like MongoDB)\r\n  * Data Source (e.g. Sharepoint or Box)\r\n\r\n\r\n### **2.1 Configuring Embedding Models**\r\n[Section titled \u201c2.1 Configuring Embedding Models\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#21-configuring-embedding-models)\r\n  * **Embedding model API Key Management** : Configure Embedding Model connection as a shared project resource. When creating an Index, a user can select from a dropdown the already configured API key instead of entering credentials manually.\r\n\r\n\r\n### **2.2 Data Sources and Data Sinks**\r\n[Section titled \u201c2.2 Data Sources and Data Sinks\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#22-data-sources-and-data-sinks)\r\n  * **Pre-configure Data Source Connectors** : Use a service credential to provide controlled access to shared folders.\r\n  * Pre-Configure Data Sink Connection\r\n  * When creating an index, users can select Data Source and Data Sink from a dropdown list\r\n\r\n\r\n## **Step 3: Defining Users and Roles**\r\n[Section titled \u201cStep 3: Defining Users and Roles\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#step-3-defining-users-and-roles)\r\nIn Settings \u2192 Members you can add team members to your organization. By default, LlamaCloud has two roles: **Admin** and **Viewer**. We plan to add additional roles for granular control.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2068, "end_char_idx": 4050, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "1d1f14a7-6287-45c7-9df2-c00ddf32740a", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "72468f3a-25ff-41ab-8738-02dedc44d20f", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "b8c39dae2cacf893210786c92b0b022cd8e1ef9c9eefaacca37796940313a1e7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "0812141d-b198-4b6d-872f-4b4f1803352d", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "0ba8402d5560fd97af6a13c945af24e1e84224e1c216d48d1286f2fea5fd5351", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "By default, LlamaCloud has two roles: **Admin** and **Viewer**. We plan to add additional roles for granular control.\r\n## **Step 4: Enterprise Rollout Strategy**\r\n[Section titled \u201cStep 4: Enterprise Rollout Strategy\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#step-4-enterprise-rollout-strategy)\r\n### **4.1 Phase 1: Pilot Group Deployment**\r\n[Section titled \u201c4.1 Phase 1: Pilot Group Deployment\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#41-phase-1-pilot-group-deployment)\r\n  * Start with a small team of **10-25 pilot users** in the `Experiments` project.\r\n  * Gather feedback on usability, security, and role assignments.\r\n\r\n\r\n### **4.2 Phase 2: Teams Expansion**\r\n[Section titled \u201c4.2 Phase 2: Teams Expansion\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#42-phase-2-teams-expansion)\r\n  * Roll out LlamaCloud to various teams (or use cases) by creating projects for each.\r\n  * Configure resources for each project so that the Index creation process is seamless", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3933, "end_char_idx": 5006, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "61e1e5c8-ad49-41de-89de-9e110f84f2a9", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "7b70a3a3-8240-4559-b5a5-903ed4bfe547", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "f55f85b8027654eb9b9ed855ea4f630f32551e8a35439b9861e84a973fe14397", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "dd92d986-cbfd-49ec-b358-d785c81562ce", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "dfb5f777075be1099bda7222465df10a461a8ffec10a9e95a60262d44a690f93", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "[Skip to content](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/api_key/#_top)\r\n# API Key\r\nCopy as Markdown\r\nMCP Server\r\nCopy MCP URL  [ Install in Cursor ](cursor://anysphere.cursor-deeplink/mcp/install?name=llama-index-docs&config=eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2RldmVsb3BlcnMubGxhbWFpbmRleC5haS9tY3AifQ==) Copy Claude config  Copy Codex config \r\nYou need an API key to use LlamaCloud services including Parse, Extract, and Index.\r\n## Generate a New API Key\r\n[Section titled \u201cGenerate a New API Key\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/api_key/#generate-a-new-api-key)\r\n  1. Go to [LlamaCloud](https://cloud.llamaindex.ai) and sign in with your preferred method.\r\n  2. Click on \u201cAPI Key\u201d in the left sidebar navigation.\r\n  3. Click the \u201cGenerate New Key\u201d button.\r\nAccess the API Key page\r\n  4. Enter a descriptive name for your key and click \u201cCreate new key\u201d.\r\n  5. **Important** : Copy your API key immediately. For security reasons, you won\u2019t be able to view the full key after you leave this page.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 1019, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "dd92d986-cbfd-49ec-b358-d785c81562ce", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "7b70a3a3-8240-4559-b5a5-903ed4bfe547", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "f55f85b8027654eb9b9ed855ea4f630f32551e8a35439b9861e84a973fe14397", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "61e1e5c8-ad49-41de-89de-9e110f84f2a9", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "cfaca116c8fac36078d7320d92768c60e111216be1113a335b1ec6d7e79c394c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "263edefc-0f84-428b-94c8-a43072de6751", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "3f75743a54cc989db3b0a10c68eae0ea37dcf6b48d8b6dcf109a30b6329cf84f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Enter a descriptive name for your key and click \u201cCreate new key\u201d.\r\n  5. **Important** : Copy your API key immediately. For security reasons, you won\u2019t be able to view the full key after you leave this page.\r\nGenerate your key\r\n\r\n\r\n## Managing Your API Keys\r\n[Section titled \u201cManaging Your API Keys\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/api_key/#managing-your-api-keys)\r\nYou can manage all your API keys from the API Key page:\r\n  * **View active keys** : See all currently active keys and when they were created\r\n  * **Revoke keys** : If a key is compromised or no longer needed, you can instantly revoke it\r\n  * **Create new keys** : Generate additional keys for different projects or environments\r\n\r\nThe UI lets you manage your keys\r\n## Using Your API Key\r\n[Section titled \u201cUsing Your API Key\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/api_key/#using-your-api-key)\r\nEach LlamaCloud product has specific instructions for using your API key:\r\n  * [Parse usage instructions](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/llamaparse/getting_started/)\r\n  * [Extract usage instructions](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/llamaextract/getting_started/)\r\n  * [Index usage instructions](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/llamacloud/getting_started/)\r\n\r\n\r\n## API Key Scope\r\n[Section titled \u201cAPI Key Scope\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/api_key/#api-key-scope)\r\nAPI keys in LlamaCloud are scoped to both the individual user and the project:\r\n  * **User Scope** : Each API key is associated with the user who created it\r\n  * **Project Scope** : Keys are tied to the specific project they were created in and cannot be used across different projects\r\n\r\n\r\nThis scoping ensures proper access control and usage tracking within your organization.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 813, "end_char_idx": 2623, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "263edefc-0f84-428b-94c8-a43072de6751", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "7b70a3a3-8240-4559-b5a5-903ed4bfe547", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "f55f85b8027654eb9b9ed855ea4f630f32551e8a35439b9861e84a973fe14397", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "dd92d986-cbfd-49ec-b358-d785c81562ce", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "f27fbf71489e2e6aa2961aa2e9402a735f44bec7c3430758d210ec1ecf01f37f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "## Security Best Practices\r\n[Section titled \u201cSecurity Best Practices\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/api_key/#security-best-practices)\r\n  * **Never hardcode your API key** directly in your application code\r\n  * Store API keys as environment variables or in a secure key management service\r\n  * Rotate your keys periodically for enhanced security\r\n  * Use different keys for development and production environments", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2625, "end_char_idx": 3062, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "2925c311-9e92-4daa-8fd8-0e836f80dbc5", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3885, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "da562515-7fdb-4d35-856a-c98625a7045c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3885, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "debb097cca5ea336883f936682c0c3aafbd35a009bd47e1c332e9651a06cf5d4", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "af3a2d61-5fd7-4387-9f49-3619044cb81b", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ef5e3e5621814aaf38de1a09eff9573dc76050b15131c05c3bbf6f4f9930f416", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "[Skip to content](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#_top)\r\n# Billing and Usage\r\nCopy as Markdown\r\nMCP Server\r\nCopy MCP URL  [ Install in Cursor ](cursor://anysphere.cursor-deeplink/mcp/install?name=llama-index-docs&config=eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2RldmVsb3BlcnMubGxhbWFpbmRleC5haS9tY3AifQ==) Copy Claude config  Copy Codex config \r\nLlamaCloud is a subscription-based service. You can manage all billing and usage from the Settings section in your [LlamaCloud dashboard](https://cloud.llamaindex.ai/). You can learn more about pricing in the [Pricing](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/pricing) page.\r\n## Accessing Billing Settings\r\n[Section titled \u201cAccessing Billing Settings\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#accessing-billing-settings)\r\nYou can access billing and plan management in two ways:\r\n  1. **Quick upgrade** : Click the \u201cUpgrade now\u201d button in the bottom left of your dashboard for immediate plan selection\r\n  2. **Full billing management** : Click \u201cSettings\u201d in the left sidebar, then navigate to the \u201cBilling\u201d tab for comprehensive billing options\r\n\r\n\r\n## Managing Your Plan\r\n[Section titled \u201cManaging Your Plan\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#managing-your-plan)\r\n### Viewing Current Plan and Upgrading\r\n[Section titled \u201cViewing Current Plan and Upgrading\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#viewing-current-plan-and-upgrading)\r\nIn the Settings \u2192 Billing \u2192 Pricing section, you can view your current plan and available upgrade options. LlamaCloud offers several plans:\r\n  * **Free Plan** : $0/month with 10k credits\r\n  * **Starter Plan** : $50/month with 40k credits\r\n  * **Pro Plan** : $500/month with 400k credits\r\n  * **Enterprise Plan** : Custom pricing with dedicated features\r\n\r\n\r\nTo upgrade your plan, click the \u201cUpgrade\u201d button on your desired plan.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 1909, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "af3a2d61-5fd7-4387-9f49-3619044cb81b", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3885, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "da562515-7fdb-4d35-856a-c98625a7045c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3885, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "debb097cca5ea336883f936682c0c3aafbd35a009bd47e1c332e9651a06cf5d4", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "2925c311-9e92-4daa-8fd8-0e836f80dbc5", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3885, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "6d50cd6682caeef7e4bd403788be13c965ae6dc91d81f87c988ccdd8b55a8747", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "You\u2019ll be prompted to enter payment details and confirm the upgrade. Your new plan takes effect immediately.\r\n### Downgrading Your Plan\r\n[Section titled \u201cDowngrading Your Plan\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#downgrading-your-plan)\r\nYou can downgrade to the Free plan at any time by managing your subscription in the Pricing section. Click on your current plan\u2019s settings to access cancellation options.\r\n## Monitoring Usage\r\n[Section titled \u201cMonitoring Usage\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#monitoring-usage)\r\n### Real-time Usage Tracking\r\n[Section titled \u201cReal-time Usage Tracking\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#real-time-usage-tracking)\r\nNavigate to Settings \u2192 Billing \u2192 Usage to view detailed usage analytics. This section shows:\r\n  * Current credit usage against your monthly quota\r\n  * Usage breakdown by parsing mode (Audio Seconds, Chart Parsing, Extraction, etc.)\r\n  * Historical usage trends with interactive charts\r\n\r\n\r\nYou can also access real-time usage data [via the API](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/cloud-api-reference/get-project-usage-api-v-1-projects-project-id-usage-get) for programmatic monitoring.\r\n## Invoice Management\r\n[Section titled \u201cInvoice Management\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#invoice-management)\r\n### Viewing Billing History\r\n[Section titled \u201cViewing Billing History\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#viewing-billing-history)\r\nYour complete invoice history is available in Settings \u2192 Billing \u2192 Invoices. This section displays:\r\n  * All past invoices with dates and amounts\r\n  * Invoice status (Draft, Issued, Paid)\r\n  * Detailed billing periods\r\n  * Payment method management options\r\n\r\n\r\nEach invoice can be downloaded or viewed in detail, showing exact breakdowns of your charges for the billing period.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1910, "end_char_idx": 3819, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}]}, "4f2efc62542fe7ca33a49ba08dec9fab6edfcffc0184737550356724e81123a8": {"nodes": [{"__data__": {"id_": "f33130ac-139b-47f7-8648-1f4b9af25394", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud.md", "file_name": "python_cloud.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 1518, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16", "document_title": "\"Optimizing Document Processing and Search Capabilities with LlamaCloud and LlamaIndex\""}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "71f1bc32-2009-49a2-938f-35622d6507a1", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud.md", "file_name": "python_cloud.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 1518, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "0c05e8489c835eb8b35ab4e3626950d102e3222fd2bd496ae248bef18b196884", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "[Skip to content](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/#_top)\r\n# Welcome to LlamaCloud\r\nCopy as Markdown\r\nMCP Server\r\nCopy MCP URL  [ Install in Cursor ](cursor://anysphere.cursor-deeplink/mcp/install?name=llama-index-docs&config=eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2RldmVsb3BlcnMubGxhbWFpbmRleC5haS9tY3AifQ==) Copy Claude config  Copy Codex config \r\nLlamaCloud is a hosted service for document processing and search, powered by LlamaIndex. It consists of five primary components:\r\nParse\r\nTransform complex documents into LLM-ready structured data with support for 130+ file formats, multimodal parsing, and advanced table/chart extraction.\r\nExtract\r\nTransform documents into well-typed structured data with customizable schemas and batch processing capabilities.\r\nIndex\r\nTransform document collections into searchable knowledge bases with vector database integration and customizable RAG pipelines.\r\nClassify\r\nAutomatically categorize documents using natural-language rules. Use as a pre-processing step for extraction, parsing, or indexing.\r\nBETA\r\nSplit\r\nAutomatically segment concatenated PDFs into logical document sections using AI-powered classification.\r\nBETA\r\nAgents\r\nBuild and deploy workflow-driven agentic apps with durable APIs, optional UI development, and rapid deployment.\r\nBETA\r\nSheets\r\nIntelligently extract tables and metadata from messy spreadsheets.\r\nBETA\r\nGet started with\r\n\r\n\r\n[Sign up for an account](https://cloud.llamaindex.ai/login) to get started or explore the documentation for each component.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 1516, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "[Excerpt from document]\n{metadata_str}\nExcerpt:\n-----\n{content}\n-----\n", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "aa0ee8b0-49e5-4f97-91df-81413c7cc1d6", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 1891, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16", "document_title": "\"Comprehensive Guide to LlamaCloud Services: MCP Server Installation, Configuration, and Advanced Document Parsing with Starter and Advanced Notebooks\""}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "8bdb2081-828a-4e73-8816-34dc2adb284a", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 1891, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "5d2421760d65f9c8d2d5caa919302c32645da6c40e363a75fb024730e08d2e91", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a08bb7c1-cc55-4c5d-873b-b6ac043b45c1", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f0d2540b2a2a4af8fe1d8c1134751fe56e0f15fcaea799eda0160e7a94b0db4b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "[Skip to content](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/#_top)\r\n# Cookbooks\r\nCopy as Markdown\r\nMCP Server\r\nCopy MCP URL  [ Install in Cursor ](cursor://anysphere.cursor-deeplink/mcp/install?name=llama-index-docs&config=eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2RldmVsb3BlcnMubGxhbWFpbmRleC5haS9tY3AifQ==) Copy Claude config  Copy Codex config \r\nWe\u2019ve gathered a number of cookbooks for LlamaCloud in one place for your convenience.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 429, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "[Excerpt from document]\n{metadata_str}\nExcerpt:\n-----\n{content}\n-----\n", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "a08bb7c1-cc55-4c5d-873b-b6ac043b45c1", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 1891, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16", "document_title": "\"Comprehensive Guide to LlamaCloud Services: MCP Server Installation, Configuration, and Advanced Document Parsing with Starter and Advanced Notebooks\""}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "8bdb2081-828a-4e73-8816-34dc2adb284a", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 1891, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "5d2421760d65f9c8d2d5caa919302c32645da6c40e363a75fb024730e08d2e91", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "aa0ee8b0-49e5-4f97-91df-81413c7cc1d6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 1891, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "601f7a1d51c62342f755ff90bb7e8141688ae8dae774de5c40f8ce2b20fd8b63", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Our LlamaCloud Services repo has even more examples and notebooks not included here; check out:\r\n  * [LlamaExtract examples](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/tree/main/examples/extract)\r\n  * [LlamaCloudIndex examples](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/tree/main/examples/index)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Starter Notebooks\r\n[Section titled \u201cStarter Notebooks\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/#starter-notebooks)\r\n  * [Parse your first document](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/blob/main/examples/parse/demo_basic.ipynb)\r\n  * [Create your first extraction agent](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/blob/main/examples/extract/resume_screening.ipynb)\r\n  * [Index, search, and chat over your data](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/blob/main/examples/index/getting_started.ipynb)\r\n\r\n\r\n## Advanced Notebooks\r\n[Section titled \u201cAdvanced Notebooks\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/#advanced-notebooks)\r\n  * [Use MultiModal Parsing/Indexing](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/blob/main/examples/parse/demo_advanced.ipynb)\r\n  * [Tour of the JobResult object in LlamaParse](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/blob/main/examples/parse/demo_json_tour.ipynb)\r\n  * [Asset fund analysis with LlamaExtract](https://github.com/run-llama/llama_cloud_services/blob/main/examples/extract/asset_manager_fund_analysis.ipynb)", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 430, "end_char_idx": 1875, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "[Excerpt from document]\n{metadata_str}\nExcerpt:\n-----\n{content}\n-----\n", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "9951fec0-06c6-49ce-998a-8af6e0ca11f6", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16", "document_title": "**Comprehensive Guide to LlamaCloud Enterprise Onboarding: Project Structure, Integration Setup, and Role Management**"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "72468f3a-25ff-41ab-8738-02dedc44d20f", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "b8c39dae2cacf893210786c92b0b022cd8e1ef9c9eefaacca37796940313a1e7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "0812141d-b198-4b6d-872f-4b4f1803352d", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f74a50887f5fef1d15564628f751c9d53793a1bfa0df88013f85ed990bf2a62f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "[Skip to content](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#_top)\r\n# Enterprise Rollout\r\nCopy as Markdown\r\nMCP Server\r\nCopy MCP URL  [ Install in Cursor ](cursor://anysphere.cursor-deeplink/mcp/install?name=llama-index-docs&config=eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2RldmVsb3BlcnMubGxhbWFpbmRleC5haS9tY3AifQ==) Copy Claude config  Copy Codex config \r\n## **Overview**\r\n[Section titled \u201cOverview\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#overview)\r\nRolling out LlamaCloud in a large enterprise requires planning to ensure a seamless onboarding experience for users. This guide provides step-by-step instructions for configuring LlamaCloud for an enterprise environment, defining user roles, setting up integrations, and best practices for operationalizing LlamaCloud in production.\r\nNote that we will be expanding our RBAC offerings, and this cookbook will evolve with additional features\r\n## **Step 1: Setting Up Your Organization**\r\n[Section titled \u201cStep 1: Setting Up Your Organization\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#step-1-setting-up-your-organization)\r\nLlamaCloud structures access and resources using **Organizations** and **Projects**.\r\n### **1.1 Create a Central Organization**\r\n[Section titled \u201c1.1 Create a Central Organization\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#11-create-a-central-organization)\r\n  * Navigate to **Settings**\r\n  * Define a single **organization** for your enterprise (e.g., ACME instead of each user having their own organization).\r\n  * As you scale, you can consider additional organizations. We have seen large enterprises create an organization per business unit.\r\n\r\n\r\n### **1.2 Configure Projects for Departments/ Teams**\r\n[Section titled \u201c1.2 Configure Projects for Departments/ Teams\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#12-configure-projects-for-departments-teams)\r\nEach **Project** serves as a logical unit within the organization.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 2067, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "[Excerpt from document]\n{metadata_str}\nExcerpt:\n-----\n{content}\n-----\n", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "0812141d-b198-4b6d-872f-4b4f1803352d", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16", "document_title": "**Comprehensive Guide to LlamaCloud Enterprise Onboarding: Project Structure, Integration Setup, and Role Management**"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "72468f3a-25ff-41ab-8738-02dedc44d20f", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "b8c39dae2cacf893210786c92b0b022cd8e1ef9c9eefaacca37796940313a1e7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "9951fec0-06c6-49ce-998a-8af6e0ca11f6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "f5e5d381f861e3b737e2a26a9d7dc74465c077a653da80b504beb49e80397e7e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "1d1f14a7-6287-45c7-9df2-c00ddf32740a", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "25f324800ab1875e0d185accebf3dca766482f0bc7b3308d7a54315cec959ce4", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Recommended structure:\r\n  * **Experiments** : For initial testing and onboarding\r\n  * **Teams** : Create dedicated projects per Team (e.g., Research, Engineering).\r\n\r\n\r\nNote that integrations are scoped to a project (see below).\r\n## **Step 2: Setting Up Integrations**\r\n[Section titled \u201cStep 2: Setting Up Integrations\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#step-2-setting-up-integrations)\r\nYou can pre-configure integrations to streamline workflows for your users. There are 3 kinds of integrations\r\n  * Embedding Model (e.g. OpenAI keys)\r\n  * Data Sink (e.g. vectorDB like MongoDB)\r\n  * Data Source (e.g. Sharepoint or Box)\r\n\r\n\r\n### **2.1 Configuring Embedding Models**\r\n[Section titled \u201c2.1 Configuring Embedding Models\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#21-configuring-embedding-models)\r\n  * **Embedding model API Key Management** : Configure Embedding Model connection as a shared project resource. When creating an Index, a user can select from a dropdown the already configured API key instead of entering credentials manually.\r\n\r\n\r\n### **2.2 Data Sources and Data Sinks**\r\n[Section titled \u201c2.2 Data Sources and Data Sinks\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#22-data-sources-and-data-sinks)\r\n  * **Pre-configure Data Source Connectors** : Use a service credential to provide controlled access to shared folders.\r\n  * Pre-Configure Data Sink Connection\r\n  * When creating an index, users can select Data Source and Data Sink from a dropdown list\r\n\r\n\r\n## **Step 3: Defining Users and Roles**\r\n[Section titled \u201cStep 3: Defining Users and Roles\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#step-3-defining-users-and-roles)\r\nIn Settings \u2192 Members you can add team members to your organization. By default, LlamaCloud has two roles: **Admin** and **Viewer**. We plan to add additional roles for granular control.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2068, "end_char_idx": 4050, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "[Excerpt from document]\n{metadata_str}\nExcerpt:\n-----\n{content}\n-----\n", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "1d1f14a7-6287-45c7-9df2-c00ddf32740a", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16", "document_title": "**Comprehensive Guide to LlamaCloud Enterprise Onboarding: Project Structure, Integration Setup, and Role Management**"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "72468f3a-25ff-41ab-8738-02dedc44d20f", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "b8c39dae2cacf893210786c92b0b022cd8e1ef9c9eefaacca37796940313a1e7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "0812141d-b198-4b6d-872f-4b4f1803352d", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_cookbooks_enterprise_onboarding.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 5058, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "0ba8402d5560fd97af6a13c945af24e1e84224e1c216d48d1286f2fea5fd5351", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "By default, LlamaCloud has two roles: **Admin** and **Viewer**. We plan to add additional roles for granular control.\r\n## **Step 4: Enterprise Rollout Strategy**\r\n[Section titled \u201cStep 4: Enterprise Rollout Strategy\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#step-4-enterprise-rollout-strategy)\r\n### **4.1 Phase 1: Pilot Group Deployment**\r\n[Section titled \u201c4.1 Phase 1: Pilot Group Deployment\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#41-phase-1-pilot-group-deployment)\r\n  * Start with a small team of **10-25 pilot users** in the `Experiments` project.\r\n  * Gather feedback on usability, security, and role assignments.\r\n\r\n\r\n### **4.2 Phase 2: Teams Expansion**\r\n[Section titled \u201c4.2 Phase 2: Teams Expansion\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/cookbooks/enterprise_onboarding/#42-phase-2-teams-expansion)\r\n  * Roll out LlamaCloud to various teams (or use cases) by creating projects for each.\r\n  * Configure resources for each project so that the Index creation process is seamless", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3933, "end_char_idx": 5006, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "[Excerpt from document]\n{metadata_str}\nExcerpt:\n-----\n{content}\n-----\n", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "61e1e5c8-ad49-41de-89de-9e110f84f2a9", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16", "document_title": "\"Comprehensive Guide to API Key Management for LlamaCloud Services: Creation, Security Practices, and Utilization\""}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "7b70a3a3-8240-4559-b5a5-903ed4bfe547", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "f55f85b8027654eb9b9ed855ea4f630f32551e8a35439b9861e84a973fe14397", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "dd92d986-cbfd-49ec-b358-d785c81562ce", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "dfb5f777075be1099bda7222465df10a461a8ffec10a9e95a60262d44a690f93", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "[Skip to content](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/api_key/#_top)\r\n# API Key\r\nCopy as Markdown\r\nMCP Server\r\nCopy MCP URL  [ Install in Cursor ](cursor://anysphere.cursor-deeplink/mcp/install?name=llama-index-docs&config=eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2RldmVsb3BlcnMubGxhbWFpbmRleC5haS9tY3AifQ==) Copy Claude config  Copy Codex config \r\nYou need an API key to use LlamaCloud services including Parse, Extract, and Index.\r\n## Generate a New API Key\r\n[Section titled \u201cGenerate a New API Key\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/api_key/#generate-a-new-api-key)\r\n  1. Go to [LlamaCloud](https://cloud.llamaindex.ai) and sign in with your preferred method.\r\n  2. Click on \u201cAPI Key\u201d in the left sidebar navigation.\r\n  3. Click the \u201cGenerate New Key\u201d button.\r\nAccess the API Key page\r\n  4. Enter a descriptive name for your key and click \u201cCreate new key\u201d.\r\n  5. **Important** : Copy your API key immediately. For security reasons, you won\u2019t be able to view the full key after you leave this page.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 1019, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "[Excerpt from document]\n{metadata_str}\nExcerpt:\n-----\n{content}\n-----\n", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "dd92d986-cbfd-49ec-b358-d785c81562ce", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16", "document_title": "\"Comprehensive Guide to API Key Management for LlamaCloud Services: Creation, Security Practices, and Utilization\""}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "7b70a3a3-8240-4559-b5a5-903ed4bfe547", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "f55f85b8027654eb9b9ed855ea4f630f32551e8a35439b9861e84a973fe14397", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "61e1e5c8-ad49-41de-89de-9e110f84f2a9", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "cfaca116c8fac36078d7320d92768c60e111216be1113a335b1ec6d7e79c394c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "263edefc-0f84-428b-94c8-a43072de6751", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "3f75743a54cc989db3b0a10c68eae0ea37dcf6b48d8b6dcf109a30b6329cf84f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Enter a descriptive name for your key and click \u201cCreate new key\u201d.\r\n  5. **Important** : Copy your API key immediately. For security reasons, you won\u2019t be able to view the full key after you leave this page.\r\nGenerate your key\r\n\r\n\r\n## Managing Your API Keys\r\n[Section titled \u201cManaging Your API Keys\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/api_key/#managing-your-api-keys)\r\nYou can manage all your API keys from the API Key page:\r\n  * **View active keys** : See all currently active keys and when they were created\r\n  * **Revoke keys** : If a key is compromised or no longer needed, you can instantly revoke it\r\n  * **Create new keys** : Generate additional keys for different projects or environments\r\n\r\nThe UI lets you manage your keys\r\n## Using Your API Key\r\n[Section titled \u201cUsing Your API Key\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/api_key/#using-your-api-key)\r\nEach LlamaCloud product has specific instructions for using your API key:\r\n  * [Parse usage instructions](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/llamaparse/getting_started/)\r\n  * [Extract usage instructions](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/llamaextract/getting_started/)\r\n  * [Index usage instructions](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/llamacloud/getting_started/)\r\n\r\n\r\n## API Key Scope\r\n[Section titled \u201cAPI Key Scope\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/api_key/#api-key-scope)\r\nAPI keys in LlamaCloud are scoped to both the individual user and the project:\r\n  * **User Scope** : Each API key is associated with the user who created it\r\n  * **Project Scope** : Keys are tied to the specific project they were created in and cannot be used across different projects\r\n\r\n\r\nThis scoping ensures proper access control and usage tracking within your organization.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 813, "end_char_idx": 2623, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "[Excerpt from document]\n{metadata_str}\nExcerpt:\n-----\n{content}\n-----\n", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "263edefc-0f84-428b-94c8-a43072de6751", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16", "document_title": "\"Comprehensive Guide to API Key Management for LlamaCloud Services: Creation, Security Practices, and Utilization\""}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "7b70a3a3-8240-4559-b5a5-903ed4bfe547", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "f55f85b8027654eb9b9ed855ea4f630f32551e8a35439b9861e84a973fe14397", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "dd92d986-cbfd-49ec-b358-d785c81562ce", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_api_key.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3102, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "f27fbf71489e2e6aa2961aa2e9402a735f44bec7c3430758d210ec1ecf01f37f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "## Security Best Practices\r\n[Section titled \u201cSecurity Best Practices\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/api_key/#security-best-practices)\r\n  * **Never hardcode your API key** directly in your application code\r\n  * Store API keys as environment variables or in a secure key management service\r\n  * Rotate your keys periodically for enhanced security\r\n  * Use different keys for development and production environments", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2625, "end_char_idx": 3062, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "[Excerpt from document]\n{metadata_str}\nExcerpt:\n-----\n{content}\n-----\n", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "2925c311-9e92-4daa-8fd8-0e836f80dbc5", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3885, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16", "document_title": "\"Comprehensive Guide to LlamaCloud Billing and Plan Management: Overview of Billing Management and Usage Monitoring\""}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "da562515-7fdb-4d35-856a-c98625a7045c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3885, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "debb097cca5ea336883f936682c0c3aafbd35a009bd47e1c332e9651a06cf5d4", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "af3a2d61-5fd7-4387-9f49-3619044cb81b", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ef5e3e5621814aaf38de1a09eff9573dc76050b15131c05c3bbf6f4f9930f416", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "[Skip to content](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#_top)\r\n# Billing and Usage\r\nCopy as Markdown\r\nMCP Server\r\nCopy MCP URL  [ Install in Cursor ](cursor://anysphere.cursor-deeplink/mcp/install?name=llama-index-docs&config=eyJ1cmwiOiJodHRwczovL2RldmVsb3BlcnMubGxhbWFpbmRleC5haS9tY3AifQ==) Copy Claude config  Copy Codex config \r\nLlamaCloud is a subscription-based service. You can manage all billing and usage from the Settings section in your [LlamaCloud dashboard](https://cloud.llamaindex.ai/). You can learn more about pricing in the [Pricing](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/pricing) page.\r\n## Accessing Billing Settings\r\n[Section titled \u201cAccessing Billing Settings\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#accessing-billing-settings)\r\nYou can access billing and plan management in two ways:\r\n  1. **Quick upgrade** : Click the \u201cUpgrade now\u201d button in the bottom left of your dashboard for immediate plan selection\r\n  2. **Full billing management** : Click \u201cSettings\u201d in the left sidebar, then navigate to the \u201cBilling\u201d tab for comprehensive billing options\r\n\r\n\r\n## Managing Your Plan\r\n[Section titled \u201cManaging Your Plan\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#managing-your-plan)\r\n### Viewing Current Plan and Upgrading\r\n[Section titled \u201cViewing Current Plan and Upgrading\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#viewing-current-plan-and-upgrading)\r\nIn the Settings \u2192 Billing \u2192 Pricing section, you can view your current plan and available upgrade options. LlamaCloud offers several plans:\r\n  * **Free Plan** : $0/month with 10k credits\r\n  * **Starter Plan** : $50/month with 40k credits\r\n  * **Pro Plan** : $500/month with 400k credits\r\n  * **Enterprise Plan** : Custom pricing with dedicated features\r\n\r\n\r\nTo upgrade your plan, click the \u201cUpgrade\u201d button on your desired plan.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 1909, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "[Excerpt from document]\n{metadata_str}\nExcerpt:\n-----\n{content}\n-----\n", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, {"__data__": {"id_": "af3a2d61-5fd7-4387-9f49-3619044cb81b", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3885, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16", "document_title": "\"Comprehensive Guide to LlamaCloud Billing and Plan Management: Overview of Billing Management and Usage Monitoring\""}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "da562515-7fdb-4d35-856a-c98625a7045c", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3885, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "debb097cca5ea336883f936682c0c3aafbd35a009bd47e1c332e9651a06cf5d4", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "2925c311-9e92-4daa-8fd8-0e836f80dbc5", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"file_path": "e:\\llamaindex\\llamaindex-docs\\python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_name": "python_cloud_general_billing.md", "file_type": "text/markdown", "file_size": 3885, "creation_date": "2026-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2026-02-16"}, "hash": "6d50cd6682caeef7e4bd403788be13c965ae6dc91d81f87c988ccdd8b55a8747", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "You\u2019ll be prompted to enter payment details and confirm the upgrade. Your new plan takes effect immediately.\r\n### Downgrading Your Plan\r\n[Section titled \u201cDowngrading Your Plan\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#downgrading-your-plan)\r\nYou can downgrade to the Free plan at any time by managing your subscription in the Pricing section. Click on your current plan\u2019s settings to access cancellation options.\r\n## Monitoring Usage\r\n[Section titled \u201cMonitoring Usage\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#monitoring-usage)\r\n### Real-time Usage Tracking\r\n[Section titled \u201cReal-time Usage Tracking\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#real-time-usage-tracking)\r\nNavigate to Settings \u2192 Billing \u2192 Usage to view detailed usage analytics. This section shows:\r\n  * Current credit usage against your monthly quota\r\n  * Usage breakdown by parsing mode (Audio Seconds, Chart Parsing, Extraction, etc.)\r\n  * Historical usage trends with interactive charts\r\n\r\n\r\nYou can also access real-time usage data [via the API](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/cloud-api-reference/get-project-usage-api-v-1-projects-project-id-usage-get) for programmatic monitoring.\r\n## Invoice Management\r\n[Section titled \u201cInvoice Management\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#invoice-management)\r\n### Viewing Billing History\r\n[Section titled \u201cViewing Billing History\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#viewing-billing-history)\r\nYour complete invoice history is available in Settings \u2192 Billing \u2192 Invoices. This section displays:\r\n  * All past invoices with dates and amounts\r\n  * Invoice status (Draft, Issued, Paid)\r\n  * Detailed billing periods\r\n  * Payment method management options\r\n\r\n\r\nEach invoice can be downloaded or viewed in detail, showing exact breakdowns of your charges for the billing period.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1910, "end_char_idx": 3819, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "[Excerpt from document]\n{metadata_str}\nExcerpt:\n-----\n{content}\n-----\n", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}]}, "daedc6a7dd7666e009e6aeff50063fa97825aa6d4c5ad176122834cf6ddfaa34": {"nodes": [{"__data__": {"id_": "f33130ac-139b-47f7-8648-1f4b9af25394", "embedding": [-0.0026704207994043827, 0.016510389745235443, 0.02655014581978321, -0.041853711009025574, 0.03512630611658096, 0.0015069262590259314, -0.006499521899968386, 0.033405937254428864, -0.022377613931894302, 0.012010474689304829, -0.002639929298311472, -0.01911661960184574, -0.0038515685591846704, -0.056130193173885345, 0.00676592206582427, 0.049582526087760925, 0.0011546681635081768, -0.0015799455577507615, -0.008685287088155746, 0.06824979186058044, 0.035614170134067535, 0.016831355169415474, -0.018885524943470955, 0.04175100475549698, -0.03738589212298393, -0.022544514387845993, -0.011490512639284134, 0.005812658928334713, 0.014173772186040878, -0.04208480566740036, 0.02586970292031765, -0.042367253452539444, -0.021286334842443466, 0.01844901405274868, -0.031146351248025894, 0.021453237161040306, 0.007298722397536039, 0.013114591129124165, -0.014597444795072079, 0.004573737736791372, -0.029759787023067474, -0.04981362074613571, 0.020259249955415726, -0.03178827837109566, -0.022839801385998726, -0.01828211173415184, 0.0023237797431647778, 0.010925616137683392, -0.016600260511040688, 0.04167397320270538, -0.032507237046957016, -7.472444121958688e-05, -0.016844192519783974, -0.006945662200450897, -0.01589413918554783, -0.0431118905544281, -0.020310604944825172, 0.023122249171137