your current plan\u2019s settings to access cancellation options.\r\n## Monitoring Usage\r\n[Section titled \u201cMonitoring Usage\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#monitoring-usage)\r\n### Real-time Usage Tracking\r\n[Section titled \u201cReal-time Usage Tracking\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#real-time-usage-tracking)\r\nNavigate to Settings \u2192 Billing \u2192 Usage to view detailed usage analytics. This section shows:\r\n  * Current credit usage against your monthly quota\r\n  * Usage breakdown by parsing mode (Audio Seconds, Chart Parsing, Extraction, etc.)\r\n  * Historical usage trends with interactive charts\r\n\r\n\r\nYou can also access real-time usage data [via the API](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/cloud-api-reference/get-project-usage-api-v-1-projects-project-id-usage-get) for programmatic monitoring.\r\n## Invoice Management\r\n[Section titled \u201cInvoice Management\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#invoice-management)\r\n### Viewing Billing History\r\n[Section titled \u201cViewing Billing History\u201d](https://developers.llamaindex.ai/python/cloud/general/billing/#viewing-billing-history)\r\nYour complete invoice history is available in Settings \u2192 Billing \u2192 Invoices. This section displays:\r\n  * All past invoices with dates and amounts\r\n  * Invoice status (Draft, Issued, Paid)\r\n  * Detailed billing periods\r\n  * Payment method management options\r\n\r\n\r\nEach invoice can be downloaded or viewed in detail, showing exact breakdowns of your charges for the billing period.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1910, "end_char_idx": 3819, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "[Excerpt from document]\n{metadata_str}\nExcerpt:\n-----\n{content}\n-----\n", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}]}}}